msgid "Mouse Usage"
msgstr "Uporaba miške"

#. Tag: para
#: mouse-commands.docbook:15
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this chapter you will be guided in using &krusader; effectively with a "
"mouse and to configure mouse gestures through KHotKeys. By simply clicking "
"the mouse you can select different sections of &krusader;. Another chapter "
"describes the selection modes, and how you can configure them: <link linkend="
"\"konfig-selection_modes\">Selection Mode</link>"
msgstr ""
"V tem poglavju vas bodo vodili pri uporabi &krusader; učinkovito z miško in "
"za konfiguriranje potez miške prek KHotKeys. S preprostim klikom miške lahko "
"izberete različne razdelke &krusader;. Drugo poglavje opisuje izbirne načine "
"in kako jih lahko konfigurirate: <link linkend=\"konfig-selection_modes"
"\">Izbirni način</link>"
